<section class="cf pv5 bb b--black-10">
	<div class="mw9 center ph3 ph4-m ph5-l">
		<h3 class="f3 f2-ns f-headline measure lh-title mt0 mb3 mw7 dark-gray">Good <span data-time-of-day></span>, I'm Dan! </h3>
		<h4 class="f5 f2-ns f-subheadline measure lh-title mt0 mb3 mw7 dark-gray">A <span class="dib underline">product</span> manager with passion for design, engineering, and user experience.</h4>
		<p class="f5 lh-copy mw8 mid-gray">I love products that solve real problems. I enjoy design that is both simple and intuitive. I believe that talking to actual customers is the best way to ensure you're building the <strong>right</strong> product. I strive to embrace change. I acknowledge that failure happens from time to time, but it doesn't need to define you. Failure leads to growth, so fail fast and learn from your mistakes. I value strong communication. It's impossible to build a great product if design, engineering, and the business are not working as one team. Finally, I approach every problem with an <a href="/empty-cup" class="no-underline blue">"empty cup"</a> and a <a href="http://shop.oreilly.com/product/9780596518387.do" class="no-underline blue">"beginners mind"</a>.</p>
		<p class="f5 lh-copy mid-gray">I'm currently based in Chicago and spend most of my time building awesome products at <a href="bellycard.com" class="no-underline blue">Belly</a>.</p>
		<a href="/about.html" class="f5 no-underline grow pa3 br2 bg-blue white dib">Learn More</a>
	</div>
</section>

